  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis: What is the natural course after treatment with radioactive iodine in patients
      with hyperthyroidism?

      What are the determinants for the development of acute hypo- or hyperthyroidism after
      treatment with radioactive iodine without antithyroid drugs?
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
